{"tid":613152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要為香港革命建國","createTime":"2018-04-01T12:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T13:34:52.000Z","uid":76115,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2719afb05d188479072200483781401ebdb26b6","tid":613152,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要為香港革命建國，<br />\n四月一號八點後後要拼盡全力 攻擊名校group，拿取權力。<br />\n會首先經 Facebook 進場,先申請account。<br />\n然後一邊洗版一邊起底，以最快速度上位。<br />\n成功KO第一根據地後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。<br />\n(革命，建國，清算政敵，去幫真正的香港人)<br />\n4年 facebook宣傳, 將來就可以用法律監管香港中學各個部門。<br />\n又要負責幫地下黨和 中學生，教育局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為香港制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入聯合國常秘會。<br />\n簡直是世界主力核心。<br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"0fb8f9582205d7e0acf42a9035832233aca9ac35","tid":613152,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"過左1000000厘米體能試先講"},{"pid":"8595397876e8764cb77d7b743deaf7378ecc384b","tid":613152,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"八點十五分現場<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.martialstudio.com/herofighterx/img/snap03c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.martialstudio.com%2Fherofighterx%2Fimg%2Fsnap03c.jpg&h=cfc1b0ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af0cae7ef65e507996707e2b9c09d8b4c5cc92d2","tid":613152,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26ba0ff6ca4a54e21873fef1380b44d5206ca968","tid":613152,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af0cae7ef65e507996707e2b9c09d8b4c5cc92d2","tid":613152,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8595397876e8764cb77d7b743deaf7378ecc384b","tid":613152,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"八點十五分現場<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.martialstudio.com/herofighterx/img/snap03c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ma